OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,FITV News approached Jersey Zoo and
OL,7,Fasked them to send these allegations
OL,8,Fto both Dr Leslie Dickie and Graeme
OL,9,FDick so all three parties have the
OL,10,Fchance to respond.
OL,12,FThe zoo declined ITV News's request
OL,13,Ffor an immediate interview but has
OL,14,Foffered one next week with Interim
OL,15,FChief Executive Officer Becky Brewer.
OL,17,FIn a statement, Chair Matthew
OL,18,FHatchwell says: "Regarding allegations
OL,19,Fabout staff behaviour, we cannot
OL,20,Fcomment on these matters publicly and
OL,21,Fhave a duty of care to all employees.
