OL,3,CSenior whistleblowers allege animal
OL,4,Cwelfare concerns at popular zoo
OL,6,F"We have been communicating with a
OL,7,Fnumber of individuals over the last 12
OL,8,Fmonths regarding concerns they have
OL,9,Fraised. We have addressed each concern
OL,10,Fdirectly with them, including an in-
OL,11,Fperson mediation.
OL,13,F"We take allegations about poor animal
OL,14,Fwelfare incredibly seriously. In
OL,15,FSeptember 2023, we asked Jersey's
OL,16,FChief Veterinary Officer to undertake
OL,17,Fan inspection into the matters raised
OL,18,Faround the sloths and aardvarks, and
OL,19,Fshe found no concerns.
