OL,6,F"We have done everything we can to
OL,7,Faddress concerns and will continue to
OL,8,Fimprove how we communicate with our
OL,9,Fstaff and provide opportunities for
OL,10,Ffeedback.
OL,12,F"The EGM (Extraordinary General
OL,13,FMeeting where a no-confidence vote in
OL,14,Fthe Board of Trustees will be held)
OL,15,Fnext month is one of these
OL,16,Fopportunities. We hope that this will
OL,17,Ffully address matters and allow us to
OL,18,Fcontinue to focus on our important
OL,19,Fmission of saving species and building
OL,20,Fon the legacy of Gerald Durrell."
